o freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Hertford married Robert Hertford of London before 1289, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1263–1314":"1263–1314","1289–Female":"1289–Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1314":"1314","before 1289":"enne 1289","1289":"1289","1263":"1263","England":"England","of London, London, England":"London, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1263–1314":"1263–1314","1289–Female":"1289–Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1314":"1314","before 1289":"ennen vuotta 1289","1289":"1289","1263":"1263","England":"England","of London, London, England":"London, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1263–1314":"1263–1314","1289–Female":"1289–Décédée","–Female":"Décédée","1314":"1314","before 1289":"avant 1289","1289":"1289","1263":"1263","England":"Angleterre","of London, London, England":"Londres, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Hertford a épousé Robert Hertford of London avant 1289, à Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1263–1314":"1263–1314","1289–Female":"1289–Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1314":"1314","before 1289":"vor 1289","1289":"1289","1263":"1263","England":"England","of London, London, England":"London, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Hertford hat vor 1289 in England Robert Hertford of London geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","1263–1314":"1263–1314","1289–Female":"1289–Desede","–Female":"Desede","1314":"1314","before 1289":"before 1289","1289":"1289","1263":"1263","England":"England","of London, London, England":"London, Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"–":"elhunyt","1263–1314":"1263–1314","1289–Female":"1289–elhunyt","–Female":"elhunyt","1314":"1314","